                        <note rend="inline" type="source">817.041/8: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to the Minister in Nicaragua</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Eberhardt</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-08-30T15:00:00-04:00"><hi rend="italic">August 30,
                                        1927—3 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>133. Your 213, August 27, 4 p.m. Last sentence. Cable briefly reasons why
                            Liberals are objecting to procedure outlined.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Castle</hi></signed></closer>
